c: 19
v: 46
t: "Nabii Ibraahim abba Aazar isi baxa Ibraahimik: Ibraahimow atu yi-Yallitteh Qibaadat derre cabtaah akaamih Qibaadah sangeltaa?atu tet buraa kee tet xaafuk raaqe waytek, diggah xeet geedanot (xeet qambisiyya kinnuk) koo Qideyyok, xer wakti yok exxeeraay inkinnah yô lih mayaabina kaak iyye"